ension of effective factors on persuasive ads. In this research, using the meta-synthesis approach, we have analyzed the results and findings of previous researchers. By doing this, the factors influencing persuasive advertising in the business world were classified in six dimensions, twenty below. Finally, based on the abundance of number of codes related to the following dimensions, the conceptual framework of the research was presented.

